Maxima crossed her arms, stood tall but the look on her face was enough to 
have made even the Constructicons cringe.. infact it did a couple times in 
the past. 

"Enough of this!"  Her arms unfolded. "Mere melee is not what it needs to win 
this war." she strode past them all as she came to the console, typing in a 
few things. "Tell me what you know? What you are armed with?" leaning against 
the console, with a hand upon her hip, she watched Blackstorm.
